<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet"href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,400,0,0"/>
    <title>Healthy Foodies</title>
</head>
<body>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato&display=swap');

    body {
        font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
        background-color: rgb(211, 227, 255);
    }

    .error-container{
        width: 100%;
        height: 750px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .error-icon span{
        font-size: 200px;
        color: rgb(181, 10, 10);
    }

    .error-text{
        font-size: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .error-text i{
        color: rgb(95, 94, 94);
    }

    .redirection{
        width: auto;
        margin: 10px auto;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: #000;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: all 0.7s ease;
    }

    .redirection a{
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .redirection:hover{
        background-color: #474646;
    }
    .redirection a:hover{
        color: #bebcbc;
    }

    </style>
    <main class="error-container">
    <div class="error-icon">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
            error
        </span>
    </div>
    <p class="error-text"><b>*¡Ha habido un error usuario!</b> Asegúrese de completar correctamente todos los campos del formulario, de usar un email que no exista y de estar registrado ya.
    </p>
    <div class="redirection">
        <a href="/signUp">Pulse aquí para volver</a>
    </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>







